OK OK, if you haven’t noticed my stories in the past. I love Labneh. A rich, thick, strained yogurt drizzled with olive oil typically served with olives and vegetables. Labneh is PACKED with protein and probiotics. The saj bread I made last weekend matches with it perfectly. Dip your heart away!
